"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d1/Arrowhead.png/36px-Arrowhead.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/d1/Arrowhead.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Arrowhead\" title=\"Arrowhead\">Arrowhead</a></span>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Bone Flute.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/fc/Bone_Flute.png/24px-Bone_Flute.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/fc/Bone_Flute.png/36px-Bone_Flute.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/fc/Bone_Flute.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Bone_Flute\" title=\"Bone Flute\">Bone Flute</a></span>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Chewing Stick.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d2/Chewing_Stick.png/24px-Chewing_Stick.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d2/Chewing_Stick.png/36px-Chewing_Stick.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/d2/Chewing_Stick.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Chewing_Stick\" title=\"Chewing Stick\">Chewing Stick</a></span>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Chicken Statue.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/af/Chicken_Statue.png/24px-Chicken_Statue.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/af/Chicken_Statue.png/36px-Chicken_Statue.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/af/Chicken_Statue.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Chicken_Statue\" title=\"Chicken Statue\">Chicken Statue</a></span>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Chipped Amphora.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/9e/Chipped_Amphora.png/24px-Chipped_Amphora.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/9e/Chipped_Amphora.png/36px-Chipped_Amphora.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/9e/Chipped_Amphora.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Chipped_Amphora\" title=\"Chipped Amphora\">Chipped Amphora</a></span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top;\">\n<p><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Dried Starfish.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/df/Dried_Starfish.png/24px-Dried_Starfish.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/df/Dried_Starfish.png/36px-Dried_Starfish.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/df/Dried_Starfish.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Dried_Starfish\" title=\"Dried Starfish\">Dried Starfish</a></span>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Dwarf Gadget.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/58/Dwarf_Gadget.png/24px-Dwarf_Gadget.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/58/Dwarf_Gadget.png/36px-Dwarf_Gadget.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/5/58/Dwarf_Gadget.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Dwarf_Gadget\" title=\"Dwarf Gadget\">Dwarf Gadget</a></span>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Dwarvish Helm.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8b/Dwarvish_Helm.png/24px-Dwarvish_Helm.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8b/Dwarvish_Helm.png/36px-Dwarvish_Helm.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/8b/Dwarvish_Helm.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Dwarvish_Helm\" title=\"Dwarvish Helm\">Dwarvish Helm</a></span>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Elvish Jewelry.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/9d/Elvish_Jewelry.png/24px-Elvish_Jewelry.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/9d/Elvish_Jewelry.png/36px-Elvish_Jewelry.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/9d/Elvish_Jewelry.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Elvish_Jewelry\" title=\"Elvish Jewelry\">Elvish Jewelry</a></span>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Glass Shards.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/b9/Glass_Shards.png/24px-Glass_Shards.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/b9/Glass_Shards.png/36px-Glass_Shards.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/b/b9/Glass_Shards.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Glass_Shards\" title=\"Glass Shards\">Glass Shards</a></span>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Golden Mask.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/7e/Golden_Mask.png/24px-Golden_Mask.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/7e/Golden_Mask.png/36px-Golden_Mask.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/7e/Golden_Mask.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Golden_Mask\" title=\"Golden Mask\">Golden Mask</a></span>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Golden Pumpkin.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/46/Golden_Pumpkin.png/24px-Golden_Pumpkin.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/46/Golden_Pumpkin.png/36px-Golden_Pumpkin.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/46/Golden_Pumpkin.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Golden_Pumpkin\" title=\"Golden Pumpkin\">Golden Pumpkin</a></span>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Golden Relic.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/37/Golden_Relic.png/24px-Golden_Relic.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/37/Golden_Relic.png/36px-Golden_Relic.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/37/Golden_Relic.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Golden_Relic\" title=\"Golden Relic\">Golden Relic</a></span>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Ornamental Fan.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/ab/Ornamental_Fan.png/24px-Ornamental_Fan.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/ab/Ornamental_Fan.png/36px-Ornamental_Fan.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/ab/Ornamental_Fan.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Ornamental_Fan\" title=\"Ornamental Fan\">Ornamental Fan</a></span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top;\">\n<p><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Pearl.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/73/Pearl.png/24px-Pearl.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/73/Pearl.png/36px-Pearl.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/73/Pearl.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Pearl\" title=\"Pearl\">Pearl</a></span>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Prehistoric Handaxe.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/07/Prehistoric_Handaxe.png/24px-Prehistoric_Handaxe.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/07/Prehistoric_Handaxe.png/36px-Prehistoric_Handaxe.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/0/07/Prehistoric_Handaxe.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Prehistoric_Handaxe\" title=\"Prehistoric Handaxe\">Prehistoric Handaxe</a></span>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Prehistoric Tool.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/26/Prehistoric_Tool.png/24px-Prehistoric_Tool.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/26/Prehistoric_Tool.png/36px-Prehistoric_Tool.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/2/26/Prehistoric_Tool.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Prehistoric_Tool\" title=\"Prehistoric Tool\">Prehistoric Tool</a></span>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"m