\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/02/Treasure_Appraisal_Guide.png/36px-Treasure_Appraisal_Guide.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/0/02/Treasure_Appraisal_Guide.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Treasure_Appraisal_Guide\" title=\"Treasure Appraisal Guide\">Treasure Appraisal Guide</a></span>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Treasure Chest.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/32/Treasure_Chest.png/24px-Treasure_Chest.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/32/Treasure_Chest.png/36px-Treasure_Chest.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/32/Treasure_Chest.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Treasure_Chest\" title=\"Treasure Chest\">Treasure Chest</a></span>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gifting\">Gifting</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Artifact_Trove&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Gifting\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable roundedborder\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Villager Reactions\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Hate\n</th>\n<td><span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Abigail\" title=\"Abigail\"><img alt=\"Abigail Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/63/Abigail_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Abigail\" title=\"Abigail\">Abigail</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Alex\" title=\"Alex\"><img alt=\"Alex Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/73/Alex_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Alex\" title=\"Alex\">Alex</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Caroline\" title=\"Caroline\"><img alt=\"Caroline Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d4/Caro