bin</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sam\" title=\"Sam\"><img alt=\"Sam Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/5/52/Sam_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sam\" title=\"Sam\">Sam</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sandy\" title=\"Sandy\"><img alt=\"Sandy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/7d/Sandy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sandy\" title=\"Sandy\">Sandy</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\"><img alt=\"Sebastian Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6a/Sebastian_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\">Sebastian</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\"><img alt=\"Shane Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b4/Shane_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\">Shane</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\"><img alt=\"Vincent Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0b/Vincent_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\">Vincent</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\"><img alt=\"Willy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/73/Willy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\">Willy</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\"><img alt=\"Wizard Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/e/e9/Wizard_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\">Wizard</a></span>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bundles\">Bundles</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Artifact_Trove&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Bundles\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Artifact Trove is not used in any <a href=\"/Bundles\" title=\"Bundles\">bundles</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Artifact_Trove&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Tailoring\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Artifact Trove is used in the spool of the <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane#Sewing_Machine\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">Sewing Machine</a> to create the <img alt=\"Shirt290.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Shirt290.png/24px-Shirt290.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/7/70/Shirt290.png 1.5x\" /> <a href=\"/Tailoring#Shirts\" title=\"Tailoring\">Trinket Shirt</a>. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quests\">Quests</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Artifact_Trove&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Quests\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Artifact Trove is not used in any <a href=\"/Quests\" title=\"Quests\">quests</a>. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Artifact_Trove&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>By multiplying the sell price of each item by the chance to obtain it, the average profit of opening an Artifact Trove without having read the <a href=\"/Treasure_Appraisal_Guide\" title=\"Treasure Appraisal Guide\">Treasure Appraisal Guide</a> is <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"472.4\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />472.4g</span>, or <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"447.4\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />447.4g</span> when the <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"25\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />25g</span> opening cost is factored in. The profit after having read the guide is <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"660.4\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />660.4g</span>, or <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"635.4\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />635.4g</span> when the <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"25\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />25g</span> opening cost is factored in.</li>\n<li>Since the average profit when breaking open an Omni Geode is <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"96.4\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />96.4g</span>, and it takes five Omni Geodes to trade for one Artifact Trove (<i>i.e.,</i> <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"482.0\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />482g</span>) at the <a href=\"/Desert_Trader\" title=\"Desert Trader\">Desert Trader</a>, you will typically lose <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"35\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />35g</span> every time you trade for one (if you have not yet read the <a href=\"/Treasure_Appraisal_Guide\" title=\"Treasure Appraisal Guide\">Treasure Appraisal Guide</a>). After having read it however, you will typically earn <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"153\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />153g</span> per trade. This assumes you sell the contents.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Artifact_Trove&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5\" title=\"Version History\">1.5</a>: Added <a href=\"/Supply_Crate\" title=\"Supply Crate\">Supply Crates</a> and <a href=\"/Ginger_Island\" title=\"Ginger Island\">Ginger Island</a> artifact spots to sources.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: Added <a href=\"/Treasure_Appraisal_Guide\" title=\"Treasure Appraisal Guide\">Treasure Appraisal Guide</a> to possible items. Can now be purchased from <a href=\"/George\" title=\"George\">George</a> at the <a href=\"/Desert_Festival\" title=\"Desert Festival\">Desert Festival</a> and traded from the <a href=\"/Bookseller\" title=\"Bookseller\">Bookseller</a>. Can now be obtained from the <a href=\"/Mayor%27s_Manor#Prize_Machine\" title=\"Mayor&#39;s Manor\">Prize Machine</a> and from <a href=\"/Pans\" title=\"Pans\">panning</a>. Can now be gifted by a <a href=\"/Animals#Pets\" title=\"Animals\">pet</a> dog with max <a href=\"/Animals#Friendship\" title=\"Animals\">friendship</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.6.4</a>: Can now be obtained from Skull Cavern <a href=\"/Skull_Cavern#Treasure_Rooms\" title=\"Skull Cavern\">treasure rooms</a>.</li></ul>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260413234431\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.199 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.232 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 7052/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 21099/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2581/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 10528/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.004/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 517 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  114.127      1 -total\n 40.18%   45.860     28 Template:Name\n 24.79%   28.295      1 Template:Infobox\n 23.47%   26.783      1 Template:GiftsByItem\n 13.11%   14.962      1 Template:Description\n  4.99%    5.697     14 Template:Price\n  4.15%    4.732      4 Template:History\n  2.57%    2.936      4 Template:Version\n  1.33%    1.514      1 Template:InfoboxSEO\n  1.23%    1.406      1 Template:Clear\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:9678-0!canonical and timestamp 20260413234431 and revision id 187775\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng        = Artifact Trove\n|source     = [[Desert Trader]] • [[Bookseller]] • [[Pans|Panning]] • [[Haunted Skull]] • [[Artifact Spot]]s on [[Ginger Island]] • [[Mayor's Manor]] • [[Animals#Cat or Dog|Dog]]\n|sellprice  = 0\n|quality    = false\n}}\nThe '''Artifact Trove''' is an [[Artifacts|artifact]] container that can be traded from the [[Desert Trader]] for 5 [[Omni Geode]]s each. The [[Bookseller]] may trade 3 Artifact Troves for 1 [[Treasure Appraisal Guide]], provided the player has already obtained the power from that book. Up to 5 can be purchased from [[George]]'s [[Desert Festival#Villager Shops|shop]] at the [[Desert Festival]] for {{Price|10|Calico}} [[Calico Egg]]s each. \n\nIt can also be obtained by [[Pans|panning]], dropped by [[Haunted Skull]]s if all [[Bundles#Vault|Vault Bundles]] have been completed, found in [[Supply Crate]]s on the [[Farm Maps#Beach|Beach Farm]] once the player has upgraded the [[Farmhouse]] at least two times, or dug up from [[Artifact Spot]]s on [[Ginger Island]]. Four or five Artifact Troves can be obtained as a prize from the [[Mayor's Manor#Prize Machine|Prize Machine]]. Five Artifact Troves may occasionally be found in [[Skull Cavern#Treasure Rooms|treasure rooms]] in the Skull Cavern. It can also be gifted by a [[Animals#Pets|pet]] dog with max [[Animals#Friendship|friendship]].\n\nAlthough most of the contents are artifacts, there are a few items, namely the [[Golden Pumpkin]], [[Pearl]], [[Treasure Appraisal Guide]], and [[Treasure Chest]],  which are not.\n\nThe Artifact Trove can be broken open at the [[Blacksmith]] for {{Price|25}} to obtain the contents inside. It cannot be broken open using a [[Geode Crusher]].\n\n==Contents==\nAll items below have an equal (3.6%) chance of appearing inside an Artifact Trove.\n{|\n|\n{{Name|Anchor}}\n{{Name|Ancient Doll}}\n{{Name|Ancient Drum}}\n{{Name|Ancient Seed}}\n{{Name|Ancient Sword}}\n{{Name|Arrowhead}}\n{{Name|Bone Flute}}\n{{Name|Chewing Stick}}\n{{Name|Chicken Statue}}\n{{Name|Chipped Amphora}}\n|style=\"vertical-align: top;\"|\n{{Name|Dried Starfish}}\n{{Name|Dwarf Gadget}}\n{{Name|Dwarvish Helm}}\n{{Name|Elvish Jewelry}}\n{{Name|Glass Shards}}\n{{Name|Golden Mask}}\n{{Name|Golden Pumpkin}}\n{{Name|Golden Relic}}\n{{Name|Ornamental Fan}}\n|style=\"vertical-align: top;\"|\n{{Name|Pearl}}\n{{Name|Prehistoric Handaxe}}\n{{Name|Prehistoric Tool}}\n{{Name|Rare Disc}}\n{{Name|Rusty Cog}}\n{{Name|Rusty Spoon}}\n{{Name|Rusty Spur}}\n{{Name|Treasure Appraisal Guide}}\n{{Name|Treasure Chest}}\n|}\n{{Clear}}\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|hate=Penny,Robin,Demetrius,Sebastian,Linus,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Lewis,Clint,Pam,Emily,Haley,Jas,Vincent,Kent,Sam,Leah,Shane,Elliott,Dwarf,Wizard,Harvey,Sandy,Maru,Evelyn,Jodi,Marnie,Leo,Gus,Willy,Krobus\n}}\n\n==Bundles==\nArtifact Trove is not used in any [[bundles]].\n\n==Tailoring==\nArtifact Trove is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the [[File:Shirt290.png|24px|link=]] [[Tailoring#Shirts|Trinket Shirt]]. \n\n==Quests==\nArtifact Trove is not used in any [[quests]]. \n\n==Notes==\n* By multiplying the sell price of each item by the chance to obtain it, the average profit of opening an Artifact Trove without having read the [[Treasure Appraisal Guide]] is {{Price|472.4}}, or {{Price|447.4}} when the {{Price|25}} opening cost is factored in. The profit after having read the guide is {{Price|660.4}}, or {{Price|635.4}} when the {{Price|25}} opening cost is factored in.\n* Since the average profit when breaking open an Omni Geode is {{Price|96.4}}, and it takes five Omni Geodes to trade for one Artifact Trove (''i.e.,'' {{Price|482.0}}) at the [[Desert Trader]], you will typically lose {{Price|35}} every time you trade for one (if you have not yet read the [[Treasure Appraisal Guide]]). After having read it however, you will typically earn {{Price|153}} per trade. This assumes you sell the contents.\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.4|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.5|Added [[Supply Crate]]s and [[Ginger Island]] artifact spots to sources.}}\n{{History|1.6|Added [[Treasure Appraisal Guide]] to possible items. Can now be purchased from [[George]] at the [[Desert Festival]] and traded from the [[Bookseller]]. Can now be obtained from the [[Mayor's Manor#Prize Machine|Prize Machine]] and from [[Pans|panning]]. Can now be gifted by a [[Animals#Pets|pet]] dog with max [[Animals#Friendship|friendship]].}}\n{{History|1.6.4|Can now be obtained from Skull Cavern [[Skull Cavern#Treasure Rooms|treasure rooms]].}}\n\n[[Category:Special items]]\n\n[[de:Artefakt Fund]]\n[[es:Cofre artefacto]]\n[[fr:Trésor d'artefacts]]\n[[it:Artefatto rinvenuto]]\n[[ja:アーティファクト・トロヴ]]\n[[ko:유물 상자]]\n[[hu:Ereklye lelet]]\n[[pt:Tesouro de Artefato]]\n[[ru:Древний клад]]\n[[tr:Define]]\n[[zh:古物宝藏]]"
    }
